'''Masculine virile nouns''' are a class of nouns in some languages, such as [[Polish language|Polish]], which refer to male humans but not male animals.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.lsa.umich.edu/slavic/dept/WebBasedLanguage/Polish/Grammar/NominativePlural/MascVPL/Index.htm|title=Slavic Languages|publisher=}}</ref> They are therefore not to be confused with mere [[animacy]].

